/* '''Trivia''' */ Batman doesn't kill his enemies, and isn't known for killing his enemies.  Vegeta does, and is.  I don't see a similarity there.
/* Behind the childhood */ It is true Broly, Paragus and Tullece are not canon, but many group them together or consider them close to canon, so "in any way" sounds too much.
Vegeta and Bulma never got married, and the Room of Spirit and Time has unknown gravity. It fluctuates randomly, and the exact level at any given time is unknown.
No speculation. Vegeta never went SSJ3, so it doesn't belong on a list of transformations he actually obtained. He never showed any evidence of being able to transform into that state.
